      *@   기준환율(CJIEX01) 조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3320-CJIEX01-CALL-RTN.

           INITIALIZE       XCJIEX01-CA

      *입력항목SET
      *   구분코드<-1:지정통화에대한기준환율정보를조회
           MOVE  CO-CHA-1              TO  XCJIEX01-I-DSTCD
      *   그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD    TO  XCJIEX01-I-GROUP-CO-CD
      *   출력구분코드<-1:통화코드일련번호순으로오름차순정렬
           MOVE  CO-CHA-1              TO  XCJIEX01-I-OUTPT-DSTCD
      *   유효년월일－기준년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-I-BASE-YMD       TO  XCJIEX01-I-BASE-YMD
      *   통화코드
           MOVE  CO-CHA-USD            TO  XCJIEX01-I-CNCYCD
      *   환율적용회차
           MOVE  CO-NUM-1              TO  XCJIEX01-I-EXRT-APLY-NTH

      *공통 UTILITY CALL
          #DYCALL   CJIEX01  YCCOMMON-CA  XCJIEX01-CA

      * RETURN 정보 확인
           IF  XCJIEX01-R-STAT = ZEROS
           THEN
      *        전신환매도환율
               MOVE  XCJIEX01-O-TELCHK-SEL-EXRT(1)
                 TO  WK-TELCHK-SEL-EXRT
           ELSE
                IF  XCJIEX01-R-STAT = CO-CHA-07
                THEN
                   #USRLOG '<---------------------------------------->'
                   #USRLOG '<1.기준일자의　１회차　환율고시　미게시>'
                   #USRLOG '<2. WK-H-I-BASE-YMD  > ' WK-H-I-BASE-YMD
                   #USRLOG '<3. XCJIEX01-R-STAT  > ' XCJIEX01-R-STAT
      *       전신환매도환율
                   MOVE  CO-NUM-1
                     TO  WK-TELCHK-SEL-EXRT
                ELSE
                    STRING 'S3320-CJIEX01-CALL-RTN오류가발생했습니다'
                            WK-H-O-CUST-IDNFR
                    DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                    #ERROR  XCJIEX01-R-ERRCD
                            XCJIEX01-R-TREAT-CD
                            XCJIEX01-R-STAT
                    #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
               END-IF
           END-IF
           .
       S3320-CJIEX01-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
